gomodel:SYNGO_417  a      owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Fig. 3: coimmunoprecipitation with PSD-95 and SAPAP, colocalization with PSD-95 in rat hippocampal neurons.\n\nNote: BEGAIN was cloned by Yeast Two-hybrid Screening using the SH3 and GK domains of PSD-95 as bait.\n\n13/4/2017 Pim\n- hotspots of PSD-95 are interpreted as synapses for this annotation.. Experimental description: BAGAIN was cloned form a rat brain yeast two-hybrid library, experiments with cultured neurons are from rat. Crude synaptosomes for immunoprecipitation were prepared from rat brains. These experiments are featured in Fig. 3\n\nLiteral form M&M\nCoimmunoprecipitation-Crude synaptosomes were prepared from\nfour rat brains.\n\nLiteral from Fiure 3 legend\nC, colocalization of BEGAIN with PSD-95/SAP90 in rat primary cultured hippocampal neurons. Rat hippocampal neurons were double-stained with the polyclonal anti-BEGAIN and monoclonal anti-PSD-95/SAP90 antibodies." ;
        lego:modelstate   "production" ;
        dc:contributor    "https://orcid.org/0000-0003-2949-9725" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0003-0662-9523" ;
        dc:date           "2017-04-13" ;
        dc:title          "SYNGO_CC_417" ;
        pav:providedBy    "https://syngo.vu.nl" ;
        biolink:in_taxon  "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/NCBITaxon_10116" .

